0.body: Venture Index: Indexing the Philippines local startup ecosystem. Our goal is to index the following: Communities Funding Services Resources Events (upcoming & ongoing) Recruitment (hiring & for hire) Contribute Your ideas, feedback, and suggestions are welcome. Contribute thru Google Forms You may send us your feedback at our Google Forms Feedback Form Contribute thru Telegram You may send us your feedback at our Telegram Group . Contribute thru GitHub This website's entire source code is publicly available on our GitHub Repository . We use the Markdown syntax to write our pages. To suggest an edit on specific pages, just click the top-right edit button of that page. Submitting your proposed changes will create a "pull-request" which we will review. Once approved by us, your proposed changes will be immediately reflected in our website. You may check our repository's GitHub Actions tab to view the latest build progress and status. You may also create issues at our repository's GitHub Issues tab. Thank you.
